data.description: Beautiful countryside estate located in The Summit addition. This large 4 bed, 3 bath, plus study room home includes a 3 car garage on just shy of an acre lot.  Located in the sought after Deer Creek school district, yet is in minutes of all that Edmond has to offer.  Open concept kitchen with granite island, two kitchen sinks, double ovens  and spacious living area with a cozy fireplace.  Main bedroom has double sinks with large walk in tiled shower and a huge walk in closet.  Spacious fenced yard with an underground storm shelter, well pump, and this home is set up for a generator.
